6) implemented transaction in mongoDB by crating Start session then startTransaction and commitTransaction for safe and secure transaction for avoid missing out of transactoin on any side 
7) used mongoDB atlas to store databse or else in mongodb compass it was throwing an error "Transaction numbers are only allowed on a replica set member or mongos", to fix this error in compass we have to create replicaset